WEBVTT

00:02.208 --> 00:05.264
Hello, Hideaway Restaurant. How may I help you?

00:05.673 --> 00:08.128
Hello there, do I have to make a reservation?

00:08.633 --> 00:09.362
Yes, ma'am.

00:09.741 --> 00:14.173
Then, I'd like to make a reservation for dinner there next Sunday night.

00:14.809 --> 00:18.915
Next Sunday night? I'm sorry, it's already full.

00:19.479 --> 00:22.287
Then, can I make a reservation for next Saturday?

00:22.667 --> 00:24.182
Is 8:30 available?

00:24.854 --> 00:28.718
Yes, 8:30 is fine. And for how many people?

00:29.119 --> 00:30.497
There will be four of us.

00:31.064 --> 00:32.743
Okay, you're all set.

00:33.228 --> 00:35.435
I'd like to confirm my reservation again.

00:35.857 --> 00:39.299
It's 8:30 at Hideaway Restaurant next Saturday, right?

00:39.840 --> 00:41.087
Yes, that's correct.

